    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……&lt;Dio&gt;と&lt;Mel&gt;が魔科学兵器使わなきゃ、
ダオスはアセリアに来てなかったんだな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see... So it was &lt;Dio&gt; and &lt;Mel&gt; who used the Mana Cannon... And it's their fault Dhaos came to Aselia...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ダオス戦役もなかったし、
父さんや母さん、アミィも生きてた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...If that hadn't happened we wouldn't have had to fight against Dhaos...And mom, father and Ami would be alive...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレは別にアミィのこと、
あいつらのせいなんて……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now that you mention it, it's their fault Ami ended up like that...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかってるよ。何かのせいに
しだしたらきりがないんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I understand...But it is all too easy to pin the blame on someone...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたりが魔科学兵器に関係したのも
戦争があったせい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Those two were forced to fire the Mana Cannon due to the war, too...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……その先はもう私たちが知っている
お話じゃなくなってきます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...But we don't know anything else beyond that point...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうなったら、運命そのものを
憎まなければいけなくなる、か</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Pondering about it, one can't help but blame it is what the whimsy of fate has in store for us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>運命、か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fate, huh...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_097_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、その運命が僕たちみんなを
こうして引き合わせてくれた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But it is up to us as people to adjust and overcome our fates.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
